<main class="main">
  <section class="about" id="about">
    <div class="wrapper">
      <div class="about__box">
        <h2 class="about__section-heading section-heading">About me</h2>
        <div class="about__text">
          <p class="about__text-desc">
            I am a front-end developer specialized in building React apps, based
            in Rybnik, Poland. Fascinated with dynamically rendered applications
            and global state management, I have confidence in writing modern
            front-end apps that meet today's development standards.
          </p>
          <p class="about__text-desc">
            Knowledge of tools and passion for learning allow me to pick up new
            technologies with ease and to find pleasure in mastering them. This,
            along with my inborn attention to detail, makes me celebrate the
            works on the project until the finishing touches are put, and
            appreciate the value of honest feedback.
          </p>
          <p class="about__text-desc">
            <b>Technologies:</b> React.js, Redux, React Router, HTML5, CSS3,
            JavaScript ES5 & ES6, Sass, Webpack, Gulp, Git and more.
          </p>
          <div class="about__link-box">
            <a
              class="about__link"
              href="dist/img/CV-ANG-Kamil-Mazelanik.pdf"
              target="_blank"
              >Download CV</a
            >
            <a class="about__link" href="#contact">Get in Touch</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="about__card">
          <div class="about__card-wrapper">
            <img
              class="about__card-img"
              src="dist/img/kamil-portfolio.JPG"
              alt="Kamil Mazelanik"
            />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="experience" id="experience">
    <div class="wrapper">
      <div class="experience__box">
        <h2 class="experience__section-heading section-heading">Experience</h2>
