            <h3 class="experience__sub-header">August 2021 â€“ present</h3>
            <p class="experience__text">
              I currently work at <span>Ework Group</span> where I write code on
              the frontend using the <span>React.js</span> library. Along with
              other teams, we manage a Storybook where we keep common components
              for our projects. In addition to writing new business solutions,
              we are also rewriting the application using
              <span>React Query</span> to retrieve and update data and
              <span>Zod</span> for schema validation in TypeScript. We work in a
              scrum team including frontend dev, backend dev, testers, scrum
