            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="experience__previously experience__previously-active">
            <h2 class="experience__job-header">
              Constructor/ Designer working in <span>CAD programs</span>
            </h2>
            <h3 class="experience__sub-header">2013 - 2021</h3>
            <p class="experience__text">
              Before I decided to become a frontend developer I was working on
              3D models. I worked in <span>CAD</span> programs such as
              <span>Catia V5</span> and <span>Inventor.</span>
              It was mainly in the automotive sector where I designed components
              for cars and tools for manufacturing components. I was in constant
              contact with project managers and production workers. Together we
              caught up on projects from paper to final product. If everything
              passed the tests successfully then the project went into series
              production.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
